title: Ancylolomia parentii
content:
Ancylolomia parentii is a moth in the family Crambidae. It was described by Graziano Bassi in 2014. It is found in Mozambique.[1]

This article relating to the moth genus Ancylolomia is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it.
